Body: Description: After some USB stick is connected the server didn't recognize the USB device. Some not registered USB devices are unblocked now, but should be blocked. USB device control is not working anymore for some computer. Tried to restart, no effect.

What We've Learned Updated: Customer have issues with his USB devices. 
When a USB stick is connected the server didn't recognise the USB device.
Some not registered USB devices are unblocked now, but should be blocked.

Next Steps Updated: We will gather more details regarding the issue they encounter.
Schedule a remote session to verify what cause the situation.
